title: Benchmarking The Future OOf AI Search: 2026 Insights On AEO & AI Overviews via @sejournal, @hethr_campbell
content:
Uncover the insights from the 2026 AI Search Benchmark report and see how your brand measures up in AI search performance.
AI is officially the new search frontier. Brands that don’t adapt risk being left out of the conversation.
Which brands are gaining high visibility in AI search?
How can you measure against and outperform competitor brands?
Watch on-demand to see where your brand stands in the 2026 AI search race.
In 2026, AI Overviews and Answer Engine Optimization (AEO) define your visibility and your traffic.
Knowing exactly what’s working for top-performing brands is key.
Join Pat Reinhart, VP of Services & Thought Leadership at Conductor, and Shannon Vize, Sr. Content Marketing Manager at Conductor, for an exclusive first look at the 2026 AEO/GEO Benchmarks Report, the industry’s first comprehensive study on AI search performance across 10 industries.
You’ll walk away with clear, data-backed insights to measure how your brand stacks up, using benchmarks that show where you lead, lag, and can grow in AI visibility, referral traffic, and share of voice.
Watch on-demand for the only data-driven benchmark report built to future-proof your SEO, AEO, and AI search strategy for 2026.
View the slides below or check out the full webinar for all the details.
